nodes.long_description:
Gun X는 번개처럼 빠른 총기 조립, 듀얼 매치, 스릴 넘치는 좀비 모드, 그리고 명중률을 향상시킬 수 있는 사격장을 갖춘 최고의 VR 총격전 경험을 제공합니다.
친구들에게 도전하고, 아드레날린 가득한 전투를 즐겨보세요!

{710313954840504}

빠르게 총을 조립해 우위를 점하세요.

{694093230034932}

탄약을 장전하고 준비하세요.

{689025517239866}

조준하고 상대를 쓰러뜨리세요.

{1726918094584302}

기술을 연습하고 조준 실력을 향상시키세요.

{546993334900583}

**주요 특징:**
- 총을 빠르게 조립해 상대를 제압하세요.
- 멀티플레이어 & 싱글 플레이어 지원
- 좀비 모드
- 사격 연습장
- 듀얼 모드

최신 소식을 받아보려면 디스코드에 참여하세요. (GunX-Lock n Load): https://discord.com/invite/Mf5RuEPNBn
nodes.short_description:
최고의 VR 총격전을 준비하세요!
번개처럼 빠른 총기 조립, 듀얼 매치, 긴장감 넘치는 좀비 모드, 명중률을 높일 수 있는 사격장까지.
친구들에게 도전하고, 아드레날린이 폭발하는 전투에 몰입해 보세요!

nodes.long_description:
# GunX: Build Fast. Shoot Faster. Survive the Impossible
GunX is a fast-paced VR shooter built around **precision gun assembly**, high-pressure combat, and intense multiplayer duels. Every fight begins with gun parts and your ability to put a weapon together before anyone else.

{3015904115207924}




Snap parts into place, rack the slide, load your magazine, and unleash chaos in **PvP, Zombie campaign**, or master the weapon in Shooting Range. Whether you’re battling players across the world or fighting back-to-back with a friend against waves of the undead, GunX keeps your adrenaline spiking from the moment you enter the arena.

{1124549758651754}

# Online PvP (Duels)
{1871748116843427}
- Each round starts with a random weapon both players must build.
- Build fast, load up, and eliminate your opponent to score points.
- First player to win best of 3 rounds claims victory.

# Campaign: Zombies and Co-Op
{875429488346849}
- Survive relentless waves of zombies in an action-packed campaign.
- Start with basic weapons and unlock stronger guns and upgrades as you progress.
- Face increasingly fast, wild, and deadly enemies each round.
- Use special tools like Molotovs, Pipe Bombs, and Shields to stay alive.
{894335206477158}
- Play solo or in 2-player co-op mode.
- Each player has their own assembly desk and resources to manage.
- Coordinate through in-game voice chat, split tasks, and survive together.

GunX isn’t just another VR shooter — it’s a **test of skill, speed, and nerves**.

{1316521856197424}
nodes.short_description: Get ready for the ultimate VR Gun assembling experience with PvP Duels, Zombie Campaign and a Shooting Range for perfecting your assembling speed and accuracy. Challenge your friends or join them in co-op and immerse yourself in an adrenaline-fueled fight.

Mach dich bereit für das ultimative VR-Schießerlebnis mit blitzschnellen Waffenmontagen, Duellkämpfen, einem rasanten Zombie-Modus und einem Schießstand, um dein Ziel zu perfektionieren. Fordere deine Freunde heraus und tauche ein in einen adrenalingeladenen Kampf.

究極のVRガンシューティング体験に備えよう！
超高速の銃組み立て、デュエルマッチ、白熱のゾンビモード、そして射撃練習場でエイムを磨こう。
友達に挑戦して、アドレナリン全開のバトルに飛び込め！

Prepárate para la experiencia definitiva de disparos en VR, con ensamblajes de armas ultrarrápidos, duelos cara a cara, un modo frenético de zombis y un campo de tiro para perfeccionar tu puntería. Reta a tus amigos y sumérgete en una batalla llena de adrenalina.

准备好迎接终极VR射击体验吧！
在这里，你将体验到闪电般快速的枪械组装、激烈的对决模式、疯狂的僵尸模式以及射击场来提升你的精准度。
挑战你的朋友，沉浸在充满肾上腺素的战斗中！

Приготовьтесь к ультимативному VR-опыту стрельбы, с молниеносной сборкой оружия, дуэльными сражениями, безумным зомби-режимом и стрельбищем для оттачивания вашей меткости. Бросьте вызов друзьям и погрузитесь в бой, полный адреналина.

Préparez-vous à vivre l’expérience VR ultime de tir, avec des assemblages d’armes ultra-rapides, des duels intenses, un mode zombie frénétique, et un stand de tir pour perfectionner votre visée. Défiez vos amis et plongez dans un combat plein d’adrénaline.

Get ready for the ultimate VR Gun shooting experience with lightning-fast gun assemblies, Duel Matches, frantic Zombie Mode, competitive Online & Single Player play, and a Shooting Range for perfecting your aim. Challenge your friends, enter tournaments, and immerse yourself in an adrenaline-fueled fight.
